# Verifiable Skills Integration Walkthrough

I have successfully implemented the **GitHub and LeetCode Integration** feature from our newly proposed Placement Intelligence plan! 🚀

## What Was Changed

## What Was Changed

### Phase 1: GitHub & LeetCode Integration
- **Backend Model & API:** Expanded [Student.js](file:///d:/project/Skill_Gap%20Analyser%20and%20placement%20intelligence/server/models/Student.js) schema and [student-features.js](file:///d:/project/Skill_Gap%20Analyser%20and%20placement%20intelligence/server/routes/student-features.js).
- **AI Skill Gap Service:** Fetches actual GitHub/LeetCode stats and injects them into the Gemini Prompt for verifiable skill scoring.
- **Frontend UI:** Added username inputs to [ProfileEditModal.jsx](file:///d:/project/Skill_Gap%20Analyser%20and%20placement%20intelligence/client/src/components/student/ProfileEditModal.jsx).

### Phase 2: Placement Readiness Score (PRS)
- **Backend Calculation:** Updated the `GET /me` route in [student-features.js](file:///d:/project/Skill_Gap%20Analyser%20and%20placement%20intelligence/server/routes/student-features.js) to calculate a holistic score based on AI skill gaps (40%), profile completeness (40%), and resume presence (20%).
- **Frontend Widget:** Built [ReadinessScoreWidget.jsx](file:///d:/project/Skill_Gap%20Analyser%20and%20placement%20intelligence/client/src/components/student/ReadinessScoreWidget.jsx) and integrated it directly into the dynamic hero header of your [StudentDashboard.jsx](file:///d:/project/Skill_Gap%20Analyser%20and%20placement%20intelligence/client/src/pages/StudentDashboard.jsx).

### Phase 3: Smart Job / Internship Match Hub
- **Backend Match API:** Created a new `GET /opportunities` endpoint in [jobs.js](file:///d:/project/Skill_Gap%20Analyser%20and%20placement%20intelligence/server/routes/jobs.js). This endpoint matches a student's parsed skills against the required skills for active jobs to dynamically generate a `matchScore`.
- **Frontend Tab:** Created a brand new [OpportunitiesTab.jsx](file:///d:/project/Skill_Gap%20Analyser%20and%20placement%20intelligence/client/src/components/student/OpportunitiesTab.jsx) component and added an 'Opportunities' navigation button to the Dashboard to display personalized jobs based on match percentage.

### Phase 4: Alumni Mentorship Integration
- **Frontend Tab Customization:** Migrated the logic from [AlumniNetwork.jsx](file:///d:/project/Skill_Gap%20Analyser%20and%20placement%20intelligence/client/src/pages/AlumniNetwork.jsx) into a natively embedded [MentorshipTab.jsx](file:///d:/project/Skill_Gap%20Analyser%20and%20placement%20intelligence/client/src/components/student/MentorshipTab.jsx) component.
- Added a new 'Mentorship' navigation button right next to your Opportunities and Interviews tabs.

## How to Test

Your dev servers are already running! You can simply refresh your **Student Dashboard**:

1. **Test the Readiness Score:** Look at the top hero section. You should see a new beautifully integrated widget calculating your overall metric out of 100.
2. **Test External Integrations:** Click "Edit Profile", enter your GitHub/LeetCode usernames in the Links tab, save, and hit "Start Analysis Now".
3. **Test Opportunities Hub:** Click the shiny new **Opportunities** tab below the header to see jobs prioritized by your AI `matchScore`.
4. **Test Mentorship Connect:** Click the **Mentorship** tab to connect seamlessly with alumni in your dream companies.

> [!TIP]
> The Placement Readiness Score updates dynamically. Need a higher score? Try uploading a resume or filling out more of your profile data to see it climb!

